OL,6,FVitor Pereira has been appointed as
OL,7,Fthe new Head Coach of Wolverhampton
OL,8,FWanderers following the sacking of
OL,9,FGary O'Neil.
OL,11,FThe 56-year-old has signed an 18-month
OL,12,Fdeal with the club, as he departs
OL,13,FSaudi Pro League team Al Shabab.
