OL,6,FReacting to the announcement, Chairman
OL,7,FJeff Shi said: "We are delighted to
OL,8,Fwelcome Vitor Pereira to Wolves as the
OL,9,Fnew head coach of our men's first-
OL,10,Fteam. Vitor is a highly respected and
OL,11,Fexperienced coach who has achieved
OL,12,Fsuccess across different leagues and
OL,13,Fwill bring a new approach for the test
OL,14,Fahead.
