OL,6,F"This is a challenging moment for the
OL,7,Fclub, and we want to thank Vitor for
OL,8,Ftaking on this responsibility. We have
OL,9,Ffull confidence in his ability to
OL,10,Fguide us back on track, alongside the
OL,11,Fplayers and staff, and the entire club
OL,12,Fwill be united in supporting him to
OL,13,Fachieve success."
OL,15,FO'Neil's sacking followed the Black
OL,16,FCountry club's fourth defeat in a row
OL,17,Fin the Premier League at home to
OL,18,FIpswich Town.
