OL,3,CWolves appoint Vitor Pereira as new
OL,4,CHead Coach
OL,6,FThe visitors were searching for their
OL,7,Ffirst league win this season and it
OL,8,Fcame through some lapse defending,
OL,9,Fwhich lead to an own goal by Matt
OL,10,FDoherty.
OL,12,FWolves came back into it thanks to
OL,13,FBrazilian Matheus Chuna but O'Neil's
OL,14,Fside couldn't hold on and in the 94th
OL,15,Fminute Jack Taylor was unmarked in the
OL,16,Fbox to nod in the winner for Ipswich.
OL,18,FThat marked the end of the line for
OL,19,Fthe 41-year-old who left his role the
OL,20,Fnext day - and the club second bottom
OL,21,Fwith only two wins and on nine points.
