OL,6,FNot long after reports emerged that
OL,7,Fthe club's board had already made
OL,8,Ftheir move to bring in his replacement.
OL,10,FPereria's name was widely touted as
OL,11,Fthe man to be in the dugout for Wolves
OL,12,Fgame against Leicester City on Sunday
OL,13,F22 December.
OL,15,FHe mainly had an amateur playing
OL,16,Fcareer, and decided to try his hand at
OL,17,Fcoaching at the age of 28.
