OL,6,FIn the summer of 2013, he was
OL,7,Finterviewed for the Everton job but
OL,8,Finstead signed a two-year-deal with
OL,9,FSaudi side Al-Ahli.
OL,11,FTwo years later, Pereria was on the
OL,12,Fmove again, this time to Greece, where
OL,13,Fhe won the Greek league and cup double
OL,14,Fwith Olympiacos.
OL,16,FAfter spells in Turkey with Fenerbahce
OL,17,Fand in Germany with 1860 Munich, he
OL,18,Ftook over at Chinese side Shanghai
OL,19,FSIPG and won the club their first-ever
OL,20,Fleague title in the 2017/18 season.
