OL,6,FPereria then was in charge of
OL,7,FCorinthians and Flamengo in Brazil
OL,8,Fbefore he signed with Saudi side Al
OL,9,FShabab in February this year.
OL,11,FNow he finds himself in England in
OL,12,Fcharge of Wolves and his first big
OL,13,Fgame with the club will be against
OL,14,FLeicester City which is a cliche six-
OL,15,Fpointer in their fight to avoid
OL,16,Frelegation.
